headline: Superior Group (SGC) Reports Q1 Loss, Lags Revenue Estimates
summary: Superior Group (SGC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -145.45% and 1.14%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
